@startuml Payment_States

' ============================================
' STATE DIAGRAM: Payment Processing Lifecycle
' Bug Bounty and Its Simulation Platform
' ============================================

title Payment Processing State Transitions

[*] --> Pending : Report validated

Pending --> Approved : Finance officer approves
Pending --> On_Hold : Requires verification
Pending --> Cancelled : Report disputed

On_Hold --> Approved : Verification complete
On_Hold --> Cancelled : Verification failed

Approved --> Processing : Payment initiated
Processing --> Completed : Transfer successful
Processing --> Failed : Transfer failed

Failed --> Retry_Pending : Auto-retry scheduled
Retry_Pending --> Processing : Retry attempt
Retry_Pending --> Cancelled : Max retries exceeded

Completed --> Wallet_Credited : Funds in wallet
Wallet_Credited --> [*]

Cancelled --> [*]

note right of Processing
  Payment Gateway:
  - Telebirr
  - CBE Birr
  - Bank Transfer
end note

note right of Failed
  Failure reasons:
  - Insufficient funds
  - Invalid account
  - Gateway timeout
  - Network error
end note

note right of Completed
  Transaction logged:
  - Amount
  - Timestamp
  - Reference ID
  - Gateway response
end note

@enduml